Package: ggannotate
Title: Interactively Annotate ggplot2 Plots
Version: 0.9.900
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Matt",
           family = "Cowgill",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mattcowgill@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0422-3300")),
      person(given = "John",
             family = "Helveston",
             role = "ctb",
             email = "john.helveston@gmail.com"))
Description: Place annotations exactly where you want them to go by
    pointing and clicking. Launches an interactive Shiny gadget that lets
    you click on a ggplot2 plot to place text, labels, curves, or rectangles,
    then generates the code to reproduce those annotations.
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
